43 "Civil Penalty and Forfeiture Fund.
44 "§ 115C-457.1. Creation of Fund; administration.
45 (a) There is created the Civil Penalty and Forfeiture Fund. The Fund shall consist of the
46 clear proceeds of all civil penalties, civil forfeitures, and civil fines that are collected by a State
47 agency and that the General Assembly is authorized to place in a State fund pursuant to Article
48 IX, Section 7(b) of the Constitution. The General Assembly may also authorize the placement of
49 additional funds from other sources into the Fund.
House Bill 444-First Edition Page 15

